text: The [[Dar Qat]] outpost in [[Xen'drik]] is governed by Lord [[Ralastar]], a [[tsucora]] [[Inspired]] and powerful [[thrallherd]]. He is supported by eleven [[Inspired]] aides (including [[Harulkek]], the [[psi warrior]] captain of the guard) and over seven hundred [[empty vessels|Chosen]], who perform the important and administrative tasks in the city.
title: Ralastar
tooltip: governor of Dar Qat in Xen'drik
